---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - Your Weight Loss & Body Transformation Guide">
  <div class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-16 px-4 sm:py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
          <span class="block">About Our Mission</span>
          <span class="block text-primary-600">Empowering Your Transformation</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-gray-500">
          We're dedicated to helping you achieve your ideal body through science-backed methods, expert guidance, and proven resources.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-20">
        <div class="space-y-16">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Our Story</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-500">
              Born from a passion for helping others achieve their body transformation goals, we understand the challenges of weight loss and muscle toning. Our team has experienced the journey firsthand and knows what works and what doesn't.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Our Approach</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-500">
              We believe in a comprehensive approach to body transformation that combines:
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-500 list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Modern medical solutions like GLP-1 medications for sustainable weight loss</li>
              <li>The ketogenic diet for optimal fat burning and energy levels</li>
              <li>Strategic exercise routines and equipment recommendations</li>
              <li>Mental and emotional support throughout your journey</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Our Commitment</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-500">
              We're committed to providing you with:
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-500 list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Evidence-based information and resources</li>
              <li>Trustworthy provider recommendations</li>
              <li>Practical tools and calculators</li>
              <li>Regular content updates and new resources</li>
              <li>Support throughout your transformation journey</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-20">
        <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-lg px-6 py-8 sm:p-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Ready to Start Your Transformation?</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 mb-6">
            Join thousands of others who have successfully transformed their bodies with our guidance and resources.
          </p>
          <a href="/get-started" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700">
            Begin Your Journey
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
